    1 => array:4 [
      "title" => "initiate Vcard with function"
      "description" => """
        <pre class="language-javascript"><code>        function createVCard(contact) {\n
                    // Encode the vCard information\n
                    let vCardData = [\n
                      'BEGIN:VCARD',\n
                      'VERSION:3.0',\n
                      `N:${contact.lName};${contact.fName};;`,\n
                      `FN:${contact.fullName}`,\n
                      `TITLE:${contact.position}`,\n
                      `ORG:${contact.company}`,\n
                      `TEL;TYPE=WORK,VOICE:${contact.phone}`,\n
                      `EMAIL;TYPE=WORK:${contact.email}`,\n
                      `ADR;TYPE=WORK:${contact.address}`,\n
                      `URL:${contact.url}`,\n
                      'END:VCARD'\n
                  ].join('\r\n');\n
        \n
                    // Encode the vCard data for URL\n
                    let vCardUri = encodeURI(`data:text/vcard;charset=utf-8,${vCardData}`);\n
                    return vCardUri;\n
                }</code></pre>
        """
      "vendorId" => 2
      "statusId" => 1
    ]
    2 => array:4 [
      "title" => "Add buttons"
      "description" => """
        <pre class="language-markup"><code><!-- ios -->\n
        <a class="flex bg-white rounded-xl px-8 py-4 mt-8 cursor-pointer hidden" id="saveContactIos">Save contact</a>\n
        <!-- Android -->\n
        <a class="flex bg-white rounded-xl px-8 py-4 mt-8 cursor-pointer hidden" id="saveContactAndroid">Get contact</a></code></pre>
        """
      "vendorId" => 2
      "statusId" => 1
    ]
    3 => array:4 [
      "title" => "Detect Os (optional)"
      "description" => """
        <pre class="language-javascript"><code>function detectOS() {\n
                  let userAgent = window.navigator.userAgent,\n
                  platform = window.navigator.platform,\n
                  macosPlatforms = ['Macintosh', 'MacIntel', 'MacPPC', 'Mac68K'],\n
                  windowsPlatforms = ['Win32', 'Win64', 'Windows', 'WinCE'],\n
                  iosPlatforms = ['iPhone', 'iPad', 'iPod'],\n
                  os = null;\n
        \n
                if (macosPlatforms.indexOf(platform) !== -1) {\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactIos').innerHTML = '<p>macos</p>';\n
                } else if (iosPlatforms.indexOf(platform) !== -1) {\n
                  // ios\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactIos').classList.remove("hidden");\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactIos').href = createVCard(contact);\n
                } else if (windowsPlatforms.indexOf(platform) !== -1) {\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactIos').innerHTML = '<p>windows</p>';\n
                } else if (/Android/.test(userAgent)) {\n
                  // android\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactAndroid').classList.remove("hidden");\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactAndroid').href = createVCard(contact);\n
                } else if (!os && /Linux/.test(platform)) {\n
                  document.getElementById('saveContactIos').innerHTML = '<p>linux</p>';\n
                }\n
              }\n
        \n
        //initiate function\n
        detectOS();</code></pre>
        """
      "vendorId" => 2
      "statusId" => 1
    ]
  ]
